sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    participant Dispatch as IRQ Dispatch
    participant Handler as Driver ISR
    participant Periph as Peripheral
    participant INTC as AM335x INTC
    participant CPU as ARM Core
    
    Note over Dispatch,CPU: EOI SEQUENCE CONTRACT<br/>Context: This sequence occurs inside irq_dispatch(),<br/>after the driver ISR has completed.
    
    %% PHASE 1: Normal Execution (Màu xanh dương nhạt)
    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note right of Dispatch: Handler Execution Phase
        Dispatch->>Handler: Call ISR
        activate Handler
        
        Handler->>Periph: Clear Peripheral Flag<br/>(Device-specific)
        Periph-->>Handler: Flag Cleared
        
        Handler-->>Dispatch: Return
        deactivate Handler
    end
    
    %% PHASE 2: Critical EOI (Màu vàng nhạt cảnh báo)
    rect rgb(255, 248, 225)
        Note right of Dispatch: CRITICAL: EOI Phase<br/>MUST HAPPEN AFTER HANDLER
        
        Dispatch->>INTC: Write INTC_CONTROL = 0x1<br/>(End-of-Interrupt)
        activate INTC
        
        Note right of INTC: INTC Hardware Action:<br/>1. De-assert IRQ line to CPU<br/>2. Update priority logic<br/>3. Allow next IRQ
        
        INTC->>CPU: De-assert IRQ Line
        deactivate INTC
    end
    
    %% PHASE 3: Return (Màu xanh lá nhạt an toàn)
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note right of Dispatch: Return Phase
        Dispatch-->>CPU: Return to Entry Stub
        Note right of CPU: Restore context<br/>Resume normal execution
    end
    
    Note over Dispatch,CPU: CONTRACT VIOLATION SCENARIOS
    
    %% SCENARIOS: Errors (Màu đỏ nhạt)
    rect rgb(255, 235, 238)
        Note over Dispatch,INTC: SCENARIO 1: EOI Not Called<br/>Result: IRQ line remains asserted<br/>CPU immediately re-enters IRQ handler<br/>System HANGS in infinite IRQ loop
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 235, 238)
        Note over Dispatch,INTC: SCENARIO 2: EOI Before Handler<br/>Result: Next IRQ may fire before current handled<br/>Race condition / data corruption possible
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 235, 238)
        Note over Handler,Periph: SCENARIO 3: Peripheral Flag Not Cleared<br/>Result: Peripheral continues asserting IRQ<br/>Even after EOI, IRQ fires again immediately
    end